lead_paragraph: It all started with a dubious decision that drew heavy criticism: Baltimore manager Buck Showalter left stud closer Zach Britton in the bullpen and lost the AL wild-card game at Toronto.

headline.print_headline: Relief Revolution: Highlights, Themes From a Wild Postseason
